Why do you need to look at the yearbook

644
00:43:24,130 --> 00:43:27,480
when you're investigating Director Shin Kyeong Cheol's case?

645
00:43:27,980 --> 00:43:30,330
There's something I'm looking for.

646
00:43:32,280 --> 00:43:36,820
The culprit doesn't happen to be one of our alumni. Right?

647
00:43:37,780 --> 00:43:41,020
If that's the case, please consider our school's reputation...

648
00:43:41,020 --> 00:43:43,040
It's nothing like that.

649
00:43:44,530 --> 00:43:45,910
Okay.

